      "text": [
        "403 - وَ سُئِلَ اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: عَنِ اَلْجَرِيدَةِ تُوضَعُ فِي اَلْقَبْرِ فَقَالَ «لاَ بَأْسَ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.403 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) was asked about placing the palm branch (jareedah) in the grave,\nImam (as) replied: \"There is no issue (with it)”."
        ]
      }
